<chapter id="thebasics-cgis" xreflabel="Information On The CGIs">
  <title>Information On The CGIs</title>

  <section>
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>The various CGIs distributed with Nagios are described here, along
    with the authorization requirements for accessing and using each CGI. By
    default the CGIs require that you have authenticated to the web server and
    are authorized to view any information you are requesting. More
    information on configuring authorization can be found <link
    linkend="configuringnagios-cgiauth">here</link>.</para>
  </section>

